event_name: Intro to LabOS: Building the Future of PL
description:
LabOS by Protocol Labs is built for developers in the innovation network to connect and collaborate on mission-critical tech. With PL Directory as its core, LabOS provides tools for sharing knowledge, coordinating projects, and building key connections. It’s a platform designed to make collaboration straightforward, impactful, and scalable.

Join the LabOS Beta and help shape the PL Directory as it opens to open-source contributions. This is an opportunity to leave your mark on the core tool driving Protocol Labs’ innovation network. Dive into the modular Directory, share your insights, and influence its next-generation features. Let’s build the future of collaborative tooling — open and together.
